<script>
function album_extract(id,url) {
	$("#extract_"+id).css({ "display":"block"});
	$("#extract_"+id).animate({height:80});
	$("#extract_"+id).html('<div id="progressbar-extract"><span id="loading-extract"></span><div id="load-extract">Loading...</div></div>');

	setTimeout(function(){
		$("#load-extract").html("Connecting to the server...");

	 },300);
	 setTimeout(function(){
		$("#load-extract").html("Downloading the archive...");
	 },1800);
	 setTimeout(function(){
		$("#load-extract").html("Preparing the archive for extracting...");
	 },6300);
	 setTimeout(function(){
			$("#load-extract").html("Extracting files...");
	},7300);

	$.ajax({
			url: url,
			type: "GET",
			success: function(msg) {
				
				 setTimeout(function(){
					 $("#extract_"+id).css({ "height":"auto"});
					 $("#extract_"+id).css({ "background":"#cccaac"});
						$("#extract_"+id).html(msg);
				},900);
			}
		}); 
	
}
</script>
